@NODE "Pop and Twinbee Cheat"
When Ya See the Options Screen Press Up,Left,Up,Left,Up.Left,Left
Left,Right,Right,Right,Down,Left,Down,Left,Down,Left,Down,B.
Pfff a long one but now you'll play the easy game of Pop & Twinbee so you'll
