12 092660400009C0 Start with 3 continues
13 092660600009E0 Start with 5 continues
14 09266080000A00 Start with 7 continues
15 04887BD00002C0 Automatic and infinite continues
FOR CODES 16 THRU 19, LEAVE MENU OPTION ON 60
16 0B085100000E50 Matches are 10 seconds long
17 0B085150000EA0 Matches are 15 seconds long
18 0B085200000F50 Matches are 20 seconds long
19 0B0857500004A0 Matches are 75 seconds long
DON'T COMBINE CODES 20 THRU 23 WITH CODES 26 THRU 28
20 1A8CB010000150 Ultimate attack can be done any time the bar isn't empty
21 1A8CB140000280 Ultimate attack can be done with about 1/4 energy
22 1A8CB2800003C0 Ultimate attack can be done with about 1/2 energy
23 1A8CB3C0000500 Ultimate attack can be done with about 3/4 energy
24 1A961000000AB0 Energy bar doesn't go down over time
25 1A961020000AD0 Energy bar goes down twice as fast
26 1A8EA140000470 After doing an ultimate attack, energy bar goes
                  to about 1/4
27 1A8EA2800005B0 After doing an ultimate attack, energy bar
                  goes to about 1/2
28 1A8EA3C00006F0 After doing an ultimate attack, energy bar
                  goes to about 3/4
